{
  "stem": "14251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because these windows went out into the courtyard of the post office-- that huge courtyard with the cars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think my mother did, because, you see, it was easier for women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Men could simply not be seen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember, there's a war effort on, and everyone is in uniform, is serving in the service.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's even forget the Jewish issue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The fact that a man should walk around without a uniform immediately would arouse someone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And citizen's arrests were allowed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're not wearing your star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by this time, there were hardly any Jews in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were already among the last.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyone could ask you your ID papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, we didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We'd burned them and the star just before the attic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, because there-- you know, there are so many laws, it turns out, as you meet other people, now, from these times and in other countries.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rules were not uniformly applied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've been undergoing surprise even this year on hearing that the laws being turned around to be opposite in many other cities of Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For instance, in Poland and a number of other countries, Jews had to wear the star no matter how old they were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we've all seen pictures of children in the streets, in the ghettos, with stars on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these little children were no more than two years old, barely walking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Germany, supposedly, but in Berlin for certain, no child under six years wore that star.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course, that's why I didn't receive any restitution from Germany, because you had to have worn the star or been in the camp to receive restitution.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it's just weeks.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
